column2: "It looks like you're doing your best, but you'd best not let your guard down. Darkers are pretty common now."
"But I don't think I need to worry about you. Even as a new recruit, you've been doing really well."
"Oh, right. If you see Echo, tell her I'm looking for her."
"Even though she's a Force, she keeps running ahead all of the time."
"Hm? Echo said she was looking for me? That's my line!"
"I'm going to get back to looking for her. Thanks for the information!"
